{"tid":461421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人安慰下我","createTime":"2017-11-07T14:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T15:10:24.000Z","uid":2593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f0d5eb61787ca92b759f2004980e0b7b1c79de8","tid":461421,"uid":2593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:28:01.000Z","msg":"上兩個星期被唯一既朋友們杯葛 一堆人一齊玩淨係冇叫我（以前玩親一定叫） 但我住係佢地玩既對面房 我都唔知道我做錯左乜 一個人係外地讀書可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有班上既人睇得出我地變左，佢都有去問過佢地發生咩事。但佢地只係講因爲小誤會，係誤會既點解唔解釋？定係我自己本身係個誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed907c4580751ceb26837367bb773f1d8e2eae70","tid":461421,"uid":151309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:30:00.000Z","msg":"做自閉算啦"},{"pid":"60336a07bc44e307985b83d788c57a8942e8f444","tid":461421,"uid":148244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:32:15.000Z","msg":"開心見誠同佢地講啦, 有咩唔開心咪睇下點樣互相改變/遷就大家, 最後實可以冰釋前嫌有計傾返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf97082c884c214bd1785c3ec42ea324bc7bacf","tid":461421,"uid":2593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:33:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做自閉算啦</blockquote><br />\n已經自閉左兩個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50fd5896b76e9a4eba67f8fe0b26de2131447a4","tid":461421,"uid":2593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開心見誠同佢地講啦, 有咩唔開心咪睇下點樣互相改變/遷就大家, 最後實可以冰釋前嫌有計傾返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地好似當冇事發生過咁 聚會次數仲愈黎愈多 每次都係對面房 見到就心悒"},{"pid":"8d11216f7d7a00a6a254660ae27129c03e738067","tid":461421,"uid":127120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:55:47.000Z","msg":"安慰"},{"pid":"e6cce19b5a3c205d1f12acf6f3a084a8c26b02fa","tid":461421,"